│ 15295 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if required. It                                                                                                                            │
│ 15296 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles emission,                                                                                                                         │
│ 15297 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is actually                                                                                                                            │
│ 15298 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the                                                                                                                            │
│ 15299 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further                                                                                                                         │
│ 15300 /// analysis/transformations.                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ 15301 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle instructions                                                                                                                         │
│ 15302 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 15303 /// For example, given the code                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 15304 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 15305 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 15306 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0>                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 15307 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 15308 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 3, 2>, it will                                                                                                                           │
│ 15309 /// look through %s1 and %s2 and emit                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ 15310 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 15311 /// %res = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, %1, <0, 1, 2, 3>                                                                                                                                                   │
│ 15312 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 15313 /// instead.                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 15314 /// If 2 operands are of different size, the smallest one will be resized and                                                                                                                            │
│ 15315 /// the mask recalculated properly.                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 15316 /// For example, given the code                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 15317 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 15318 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0, 1, 0>                                                                                                                                                │
│ 15319 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0, 1, 0>                                                                                                                                                │
│ 15320 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 15321 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 5, 4>, it will                                                                                                                           │
│ 15322 /// look through %s1 and %s2 and emit                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ 15323 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 15324 /// %res = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, %1, <0, 1, 2, 3>                                                                                                                                                   │
│ 15325 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 15326 /// instead.                                                                                                                                                                                             │
